stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initialized: deploy
    Initialized --> LaunchpadStart: launchpadStartTime reached
    LaunchpadStart --> EpochBased: success<br/>(totalLocked &ge; min)
    LaunchpadStart --> LaunchpadFail: time expired<br/>(totalLocked &lt; min)
    LaunchpadFail --> [*]: all users<br/>refund()
    EpochBased --> EpochBased: processEpoch()<br/>(loop)
    EpochBased --> WindDown: admin triggers
    WindDown --> Closed: all redemptions<br/>settled
    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Initialized
        Vault deployed but
        launchpad time not yet reached.
        All transactions disabled.
    end note

    note right of LaunchpadStart
        Retail locks USDC.
        Internal receipt mapping.
        No shares minted yet.
    end note

    note right of EpochBased
        Normal operating phase.
        Async sub/redeem queue.
        Periodic processEpoch().
    end note

    note left of WindDown
        Refund pending sub.
        Liquidate liquid buffer.
        Redeem illiquid from Pruv.
        Settle redemption queue.
    end note
